College student
(Coll-edge Stoo-dent)
Noun
Definition:

1. Someone who thinks Dr. Pepper and Ramen is a legitimate option for breakfast
2. A person who finds it socially acceptable to wear Heelies and a snuggy at the same time
3. Someone who knows more about meme making than they know about their major

Synonyms:
Edgy teen, memelord, depraved individual, broke AF, semi-deplorable (but not Trump supporter deplorable).

Example sentences:
That young man posting dank memes is a model COLLEGE STUDENT; I bet he gets all the bitches, what a catch!
